property_name: 4 Bedroom House for sale in Teachers Colony
description: When creating an ad for a residential property, it's important to provide clear and compelling information that highlights the key features and benefits of the property. Here's a step-By-Step guide on how to put an ad for a residential property:Start with a catchy headline: Grab the attention of potential buyers with an eye-Catching headline that emphasizes the most attractive aspect of the property, such as its location, unique features, or selling point. For example, "stunning oceanfront villa with spectacular views" or "spacious family home in prime location."Describe the property: Provide a detailed description of the property, including its size, number of bedrooms and bathrooms, layout, and any distinctive features. Mention recent renovations, architectural style, or amenities that set the property apart from others in the area. Highlight aspects that make it suitable for the target audience, such as a family-Friendly neighborhood or proximity to schools and amenities.Showcase the location: Describe the location of the property and its advantages. Highlight nearby amenities, such as parks, shopping centers, restaurants, schools, and transportation links. Mention any unique selling points of the neighborhood, such as stunning views, beach access, or a safe and friendly community.Highlight key features: List the most attractive features and amenities of the property. This may include a modern kitchen, spacious backyard, swimming pool, garage, balcony, or high-End appliances. Mention any recent upgrades or renovations, such as new flooring, updated bathrooms, or energy-Efficient systems.Include quality photos: Include high-Quality photos that showcase the property's interior and exterior. Capture key features and highlight the property's best angles. Use well-Lit images that accurately represent the property and make it visually appealing to potential buyers.Provide contact information: Include your contact information, such as phone number, email address, or a link to your website. Make it easy for interested parties to reach out and inquire about the property.Add pricing and additional details: Specify the asking price or provide a price range if applicable. Include any additional details relevant to the property, such as the availability of financing options, property taxes, or homeowner association fees.Proofread and format: Ensure that the ad is free of spelling or grammatical errors. Use a clean and easy-To-Read format that organizes the information in a logical manner. Consider using bullet points or subheadings to make the ad more scannable and highlight key details.Advertise the ad: Once you have created the ad, consider various advertising channels to reach potential buyers. These may include online real estate portals, social media platforms, local newspapers, or community bulletin boards. Be sure to comply with any legal requirements or guidelines when advertising a property.Remember, the goal of the ad is to generate interest and attract potential buyers to inquire about the property. By providing an accurate and compelling description, along with attractive visuals, you can increase the chances of finding the right buyer for your residential property.

description:
Hill ridge villa is available for sale

6 bed rooms,
5 with attached bathroom
Terrace on 1st floor and second floor
Gachibowli is a major it suburb of hyderabad located in the north-Western part of the city in the mandal of the ranga reddy district.
Gachibowli is situated 5 kilometres from hitec city and houses several prominent it companies like wipro, sierra atlantic, computer associates, infosys and microsoft idc (Largest development centre of microsoft outside the us). Cyber city, madhapur, kollur, malkapur, patancheru and hafeezpet are some of the areas located within proximity of gachibowli. Surrounding areas include jubilee hills, madhapur, banjara hill, kothaguda, mehdipatnam, panjagutta and kukatpally, among others.
Tourist attractions in and around gachibowli are durgam cheruvu, shilparamam, hussain sagar, ramoji rao film city and golconda fort. A new it sez by dlf is also expected to be developed in gachibowli. In addition to being an it hub, gachibowli is also a sports hub. The gmc athletic stadium and a world-Class hockey stadium are located here. Gachibowli is also home to famous educational institutions including iit, indian school of business and the university of hyderabad.
Connectivity
Gachibowli is well-Connected to hitec city and the outer ring road connects it to the international airport at shamshabad. To provide better connectivity and additional transport facilities for commuters, a metro train is also being planned in the city and will be operational by 2015. The nehru outer ring road connects gachibowli to rajiv gandhi international airport and nearest railway stations are hafeezpet railway station and hitec city railway station.
The deccan railway station is located at a driving distance of 14 kilometres and apsrtc buses connect gachibowli to mehdipatnam and koti. Hafeezpet mmts train station is about 6 kilometres and hitec city station about 7 kilometres from gachibowli. To decongest traffic and reduce travel time between mehdipatnam and gachibowli, a 650-Metre long flyover at toli chowki junction has been proposed. Another important road, the old mumbai highway connecting jubilee hills with gachibowli road is being extended from 60 feet to 120 feet.
Schools and hospitals
Gachibowli houses several well-Known educational institutions like isb learning resource centre, kendriya vidyalaya, jawaharlal nehru institute for development banking, government primary school, sarojini naidu school of arts and communication. Aarogya center, oasis centre of reproductive medicine, manikanta hospital, aakruthi dental hospital and dr. Amar's dental hospital are some of reputed hospitals in the area. Continental hospital is constructing a 700-Bed super speciality hospital in gachibowli which is expected to become the largest healthcare facility in the city. Hyatt and regenta one are two of the most famous hotels in gachibowli.
